-- Brazil Police Seize Ferrari Owned by Batista’s Son, O Globo Says
-- B y   M a t t h e w   B r i s t o w
-- 2012-05-06T22:04:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-06/brazil-police-seize-ferrari-owned-by-batista-s-son-o-globo-says.html
Authorities in  Rio de Janeiro  today
impounded a Ferrari belonging to Thor Batista, son of Brazil’s
richest man  Eike Batista , for lacking a front license plate, O
Globo reported, citing local police.  EBX Group Co., the holding company for most of Batista’s
assets, didn’t immediately respond to a phone call seeking
comment made outside office hours.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Matthew Bristow in Brasilia at 
 mbristow5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Goodman at 
 jgoodman19@bloomberg.net  